data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!  There are endless possibilities to customize your dream home in this basement rancher!  The main level features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, kitchen with breakfast bar, breakfast room with bay window, and open concept living and dining room. The oversized deck overlooks the spacious, private backyard. Natural light floods the unfinished daylight walkout basement and is pre-plumbed for a bathroom. This prime West Knoxville location is just minutes to Kingston Pike and Pellissippi Parkway and is in a desirable school zone. Owner financing potentially available with acceptable offer.  *Buyer and Buyer's representatives to verify all.*
